===2020 census===
As of the 2020 census, there are 173 people living in Boys Ranch. The racial makeup of the city was 68.05% Non-Hispanic White, 14.79% Non-Hispanic Black, 0.59% Asian, 9.47% some other race, and 7.1% two or more races.<ref>{{cite web |title=United States Census Bureau Boys Ranch (Race and Ethnicity) |url=https://data.census.gov/table?t=Populations+and+People:Race+and+Ethnicity&g=160XX00US4809796&tid=DECENNIALPL2020.P1 |website=United States Census Bureau |access-date=3 July 2023}}</ref>

